name: Chewer of doubts
description: Digital synthesis of two digital works (themselves syntheses of analog works), liquidized and further worked on digitally. Sometimes doubt creeps in and can be a paralysing force if left to roam freely in the mind. It freezes the momentum of intention and life force wanting to express itself, leaving cold and dark feeling. In such moments I imagine a massive monkey king beast rising and chewing the doubts, liquidizing them back into creative potential.
